## Entry Points
- `src/main.rs` тАФ binary bootstrap
- `src/lib.rs` тАФ crate root, all pub mods
- `src/bin/installer.rs` тАФ Windows installer

## ACP / Zed Integration (`src/acp/`)
- `mod.rs` тАФ session lifecycle, JSON-RPC dispatch
- `protocol.rs` тАФ ACP message types
- `security.rs` тАФ path sandboxing
- `slash_commands.rs` тАФ `/help` `/clear` `/model` `/rule` etc.
  - `get_available_commands()` тАФ advertises to Zed command picker
  - `handle_builtin()` тАФ routes to BuiltinResult
  - `command_to_prompt()` тАФ builds AI prompt
- `tools.rs` тАФ routes ACP tool calls тЖТ `src/tools/`

## Slash Commands
- `/help` `/clear` `/context` `/tools` `/model`
- `/think off|low|high` тАФ reasoning effort
- `/goal <text>` тАФ session goal injection
- `/rule add|list|remove|clear` тАФ session-only rules
- `/commit [instructions]` тАФ Conventional Commits from git diff
- `/bayes show|reset|explain` тАФ Bayesian state
- `/diagnostics` тАФ system health
- `/visualize` тАФ pipeline graph
- `/web` `/explain` `/review` `/plan` `/test` `/fix`

## Session Data (`src/acp/mod.rs тЖТ SessionData`)
- `messages` тАФ conversation history
- `config` тАФ model, temperature, max_tokens
- `current_goal` тАФ active session goal
- `session_rules` тАФ temporary rules (SessionRules)
- `bayes_engine` тАФ Bayesian inference
- `dna` тАФ SessionDna personality

## Context (`src/context/`)
- `mod.rs` тАФ multi-file context discovery
- `session_rules.rs` тАФ add/remove/list/clear/format_for_prompt
- `belief_state.rs` тАФ runtime belief tracking
- `agent_rules.rs` тАФ loads .agents/rules/ files

## Router (`src/router/`)
- Bayesian routing тАФ belief-weighted model selection
- Starlink-resilient retries + timeouts
- Thinking mode passthrough (off/low/high)

## Tools (`src/tools/`)
- `registry.rs` тАФ central tool registry
- File: read_file, write_file, list_directory, find_path, delete_file
- Shell: run_command
- Web: web_search
- Task: task graph tools
- Agent: spawn_agent, fork_agent, join_agents

## Memory (`src/memory/`)
- 4-tier hierarchy: working тЖТ episodic тЖТ semantic тЖТ archival
- Context compression + archiving

## Safety (`src/safety/`)
- `pre_write_hook.rs` тАФ blocks binary, massive overwrites
- `dry_run.rs` тАФ diff preview before commit
- `diff_validator.rs` тАФ rejects full-file rewrites >200 lines
- `intent_validator.rs` тАФ forces clarification on ambiguous edits
- `suspicious_write_guard.rs` тАФ final in-tool checks
- `dna_safety.rs` тАФ raises thresholds on repeated failures
- `tool_health_monitor.rs` тАФ per-tool success/failure tracking

## Session DNA (`src/session/dna.rs`)
- tone, verbosity, risk_tolerance, coding_style, tool_preferences
- Injected into system prompt
- Evolves via tool feedback loop
- Drives mode: coder / research / shell / creative

## Skills (`src/skills/`)
- Auto-activation on project context keywords
- `.agents/skills/` тАФ project-local skills
- `~/.grok-cli/agents/skills/` тАФ global skills

## Engine (`src/engine/`)
- Reasoning engine тАФ plan тЖТ step тЖТ execute
- `StepAction::DelegateToSubAgent` тАФ multi-agent
- DNA-driven skill arbitration

## Multi-Agent (`src/agent/`)
- `manager.rs` тАФ AgentManager registry
- `message_bus.rs` тАФ in-memory AgentMessageBus
- Tools: spawn_agent, fork_agent, join_agents, cancel_agent

## Config (`src/config/`)
- Priority: env vars тЖТ CLI args тЖТ .grok/.env тЖТ ~/.grok/.env тЖТ defaults
- `config.toml` тАФ model, ACP, logging, tools, sessions

